>>DAVID WILCOCK:
I'm David Wilcock.

00:00:17.630 --> 00:00:19.290 align:middle line:90%
And welcome to "Disclosure."

00:00:19.290 --> 00:00:22.000 align:middle line:10%
I recommend that you
have a good cappuccino,

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.890 align:middle line:10%
