00:30:35.496 --> 00:30:38.150 align:middle line:90%
>>SCRANTON: Thank you very much.

00:30:38.150 --> 00:30:40.350 align:middle line:10%
>>DAVID: I love where we
ended on this interview

00:30:40.350 --> 00:30:44.460 align:middle line:10%
because it's the distinct
suggestion that even

00:30:44.460 --> 00:30:47.230 align:middle line:10%
though Griaule didn't
really get into it too much,

00:30:47.230 --> 00:30:51.960 align:middle line:10%
the ultimate point of what
the Dogon were being taught

00:30:51.960 --> 00:30:55.370 align:middle line:10%
was the notion of ascension.

00:30:55.370 --> 00:30:57.970 align:middle line:84%
These higher beings,
these extraterrestrials

00:30:57.970 --> 00:31:01.030 align:middle line:84%
allegedly from Sirius,
came here to give us

00:31:01.030 --> 00:31:05.360 align:middle line:84%
a cosmology that ultimately
liberates the soul from needing

00:31:05.360 --> 00:31:08.260 align:middle line:84%
to reincarnate in
this world of flesh,

00:31:08.260 --> 00:31:10.760 align:middle line:84%
coming back in each time,
forgetting who we are,

00:31:10.760 --> 00:31:12.960 align:middle line:84%
forgetting what we're
supposed to be doing here,

00:31:12.960 --> 00:31:16.830 align:middle line:84%
and having to make mistakes
and accrue karma and work off

00:31:16.830 --> 00:31:20.050 align:middle line:84%
karma and come back and be
saying you're sorry over

00:31:20.050 --> 00:31:23.020 align:middle line:84%
and over again and having to be
tortured because you tortured

00:31:23.020 --> 00:31:25.960 align:middle line:84%
other people-- they want
us to break free of that.

00:31:25.960 --> 00:31:28.100 align:middle line:84%
And there is a point
at which we learn

00:31:28.100 --> 00:31:30.430 align:middle line:84%
what the true essence
of the universe is,

00:31:30.430 --> 00:31:32.560 align:middle line:84%
and we break free
from the shackles

00:31:32.560 --> 00:31:34.260 align:middle line:90%
of having to reincarnate here.

00:31:34.260 --> 00:31:37.520 align:middle line:84%
And we graduate into
becoming light beings

00:31:37.520 --> 00:31:42.195 align:middle line:84%
and truly grasping our
essence as immortal souls.

00:31:42.195 --> 00:31:44.460 align:middle line:84%
Do you think maybe
Walter van Beek

00:31:44.460 --> 00:31:49.380 align:middle line:84%
had an agenda if in
fact Scranton comes out

00:31:49.380 --> 00:31:51.710 align:middle line:84%
