collapsed in this great flood.

00:32:49.170 --> 00:32:52.020 align:middle line:84%
And only a few of the
remnants survived.

00:32:52.020 --> 00:32:55.760 align:middle line:84%
And the Dogon gone apparently
inherited some of the attempts

00:32:55.760 --> 00:32:59.190 align:middle line:84%
